creator: Sport  Apps
descriptionHtml:
Live football scores, real-time data for live scores for the Serie A, Serie B, Coppa Italia and Lega Pro (Italy), with top scorers stats, fixtures/results and the table for the Serie A.

Notifications:
Do you wish to receive push notifications for a match? You will receive a notification when either team score during the match!

The app shows the scorers of each match, yellow cards, red cards, penalties and so forth. You will also receive a push notification when your favorite team scores!

The live football scores are updated live 24/7

Serie A contains also info regarding the italian fantasy football.

With this app you can also check all the stats for all the teams in the italian Serie A.
title: Serie A
